<p>
<h3>
<a name="discussion_post_create_generic"></a>To Create a Discussion post</h3>

<ol>
<li>
From the Project space, click Discussions on the left navigation bar.</li>

<li>
From the Project.net tool bar, click Create and the Create New Discussion wizard
opens.</li>

<li>
Fill in the fields to create the Discussion Group.</li>

<li>
Click Submit to complete the Create process.</li>

<li>
Click New Post to add the first item to the Discussion.</li>

<li>
Fill in the Required and optional fields.</li>

<li>
Click Submit when done.</li>
</ol>

<h3>
<a name="discussion_post_add_generic"></a>To Add a New Discussion post</h3>

<ol>
<li>
Click on Discussions and then desired Discussion Group.</li>

<li>
Click NEW POST to begin the Add process.</li>

<li>
Submit completes the process and the post is added to the list.</li>
</ol>